{"lemma":"مُطابَقَةُ","slug":"مُطابَقَةُ","root":"ط.ب.ق","root_slug":"ط-ب-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ب-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26337"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B7%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَابَقَ (ṭābaqa) (form III)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conformity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"matching"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"compatibility"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/mu.tˤaː.ba.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26337","headword_ar":"مُطَابَقَةٌ","root":"Tbq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"putting a thing upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over, another thing commensurate therewith:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbaqotu Aln~aEola","text_ar":"طَابَقْتُ النَّعْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., as expl. in Bd lxvii. 3,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sewed another sole upon the sole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sandal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Er-Rághib, TA.) [Hence] one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbaqotu bayona Al$~ayoy^ayoni","text_ar":"طَابَقْتُ بَيْنَ الشَّيْيَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made the two things commensurate, and stuck them together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O. [See also 2.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbq bayona qamiySayoni","text_ar":"طابق بَيْنَ قَمِيصَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attired himself with, two shirts, one over,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outside, the other;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAfaqa bayonahumaA","text_ar":"صَافَقَ بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAraqa","text_ar":"طَارَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAhara","text_ar":"ظَاهَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A &c. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zhr","text_ar":"ظهر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbqhu","text_ar":"طابقهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTaAbaqapN","text_ar":"مُطَابَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TibaAqN","text_ar":"طِبَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It suited, matched, tallied, conformed, corresponded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agreed, with it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, * K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was equal to it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was like it in measure, size, quantity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA jawaAbN yuTaAbiqu Als~uw^aAla","text_ar":"هٰذَا جَوَابٌ يُطَابِقُ السُّوَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is an answer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a reply, that is suitable to the question"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbqt zawojahaA","text_ar":"طابقت زَوْجَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"complied with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the desire of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her husband:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbqt","text_ar":"طابقت"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a she-camel, and of a woman,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, submissive to him who desired her."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbq liY biHaq~iY","text_ar":"طابق لِى بِحَقِّى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He obeyed me with respect to my right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, and hastened to render it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acknowledged to me my right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"due, willingly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbqhu EalaY AlA^amori","text_ar":"طابقهُ عَلَى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He combined with him, and aided him, to do the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he aided him to do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAbq EalaY AlEamali","text_ar":"طابق عَلَى العَمَلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became accustomed, habituated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inured, to the work."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, * TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muTaAbaqapN","text_ar":"مُطَابَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of a horse, (S, O, K,) in his running, (S, O,) and in like manner of a camel, as in the A, (TA,) means His"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"putting his hind feet in the places that were those of his fore feet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b9-  And (hence, TA) (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walking as one shackled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with short steps."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijolN","text_ar":"حِجْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}